/ Rails flash messages styled for Bootstrap 3.0
- flash.each do |name, msg|
  - if msg.is_a?(String)
    .alert.alert-dismissible class="alert-#{name.to_s == 'notice' ? 'info' : 'danger'}"
      button.close data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true"
        | Ã—
      h4
        i.icon.fa class="fa-#{name.to_s == 'notice' ? 'check' : 'warning'}"
        = content_tag :span, msg, :id => "flash_#{name}"
  - else
    .callout class="callout-#{name.to_s == 'notice' ? 'info' : 'danger'}"